<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The call to ws_receive_frame only returns a non-NULL msg when frame[0] == (WS_FIN | WS_OPCODE_TEXT_FRAME), in which case *type is set to WS_OPCODE_TEXT_FRAME. The run_usock function checks if msg == NULL and breaks if so, therefore execution can only reach the subsequent code when type == WS_OPCODE_TEXT_FRAME. The else branch (and its inner if checking for WS_OPCODE_CON_CLOSE_FRAME) can never be taken and is therefore unreachable.
</scenario>
